..............Add new customer API

Request Body-
{
	"customer":
	{
		"customer_name":"Abhinav",
		"c_address":"Nasik",
		"c_mobileno":8149506028,
		"c_email":"abhinavpatole@gmail.com"
	}
}


Response Body-
{
    "customer_name": "Abhinav",
    "c_email": "abhinavpatole@gmail.com",
    "c_id": 5,
    "c_mobileno": 8149506028,
    "c_address": "Nasik"
}



.................Update Customer Details........

Pass customer id to the following Endpoint-
http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/customers/5


Request Body-
{
	"customer":
	{
		"customer_name":"Abhinav",
		"c_address":"Nasik",
		"c_mobileno":8149506028,
		"c_email":"abhinav.patole@gmail.com"
	}
}

Response Body-
{
        "status": "success",
        "data": [
            {
                "c_mobileno": 8149506028,
                "customer_name": "Abhinav",
                "c_id": 5,
                "c_address": "Nasik",
                "c_email": "abhinav.patole@gmail.com"
            },
            {}
        ]
}


.................Get ALL Item Details....

Method=GET
Content type = text/json
endpoint - http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/items/


Response Body-
{
    "status": "success",
    "data": [
        {
            "item_name": "oppo-mobile",
            "item_price": "10000",
            "i_id": 1,
            "item_quantity": "24"
        },
        {
            "item_name": "Apple-mobile",
            "item_price": "40000",
            "i_id": 2,
            "item_quantity": "0"
        },
        {
            "item_name": "samsung-mobile",
            "item_price": "30000",
            "i_id": 3,
            "item_quantity": "30"
        },
        {
            "item_name": "Senizer CX-180 Headphone",
            "item_price": "1200",
            "i_id": 4,
            "item_quantity": "20"
        }
    ]
}

...............Add new Item

Method = POST
Content Type = Application/json
endpoint - http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/items/


Request Body-
{
	"item":
	{
		"item_name":"Senizer Headphone",
		"item_quantity":"20",
		"item_price":"999"
	}
}

Response Body-
{
    "status": "success",
    "Item": {
        "item_name": "Senizer Headphone",
        "item_price": "999",
        "i_id": 4,
        "item_quantity": "20"
    }
}

...................Update Item Details.

Pass item id to the following Endpoint-
Method = POST
Content Type = Application/json
endpoint = http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/orders/2


Request Body-
{
	"item":
	{
		"item_name":"Senizer CX-180 Headphone",
		"item_quantity":"15",
		"item_price":"1200"
	}
}


Response Body-
{
    "status": "success",
    "Item": {
        "item_price": "1200",
        "i_id": 4,
        "item_name": "Senizer CX-180 Headphone",
        "item_quantity": "20"
    }
}



