..............Sale Item to the customer
Method = POST
Content Type - Application/json
endpoint - http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/orders/

Request Body-
{
	"order":
	{
		"c_id":5,
		"i_id":4,
		"sale_quantity":"2"
	}
}

Response Body-
{
    "status": "success",
    "Order": [
        {
            "Item": {
                "i_id": 4,
                "c_id": 5,
                "sale_quantity": "2"
            }
        },
        {
            "customer": {
                "i_id": 4,
                "c_id": 5,
                "sale_quantity": "2"
            }
        },
        {
            "bill": {
                "i_id": 4,
                "bill_amount": "1998",
                "c_id": 5
            }
        }
    ]
}



.....................Login API

Authentication Type - Basic Authentication
Method = GET
Endpoint - http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/login/

Request Body...............
{
	"user":
	{
		"username":"Manish123",
		"password":"Prashant123",
		"role":"admin"
	}
}


Response Body -
{
    "User": [
        {
            "id": 2,
            "password": "pbkdf2:sha256:50000$3QLO1eMy$661c71730bf9a899416f31f977896e20469da0764d28e6a745c18b057728d30f",
            "role": "admin",
            "username": "Manish123"
        }
    ]
    "status": "success"
}



